	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm going to test out the portability of my library soon.  I've got an intel Mac and a PPC Mac to test this on.  I can also test this on Windows with Cygwin but I don't see the point of that.
<br />
<br />If anybody has tested libcopynes and bcn on any platform other than i386 Linux, please let me know.  I'm most curious about other "POSIX" platforms like FreeBSD and OpenBSD.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


